\section{Belt calculations}

For an endless belt, what is the circumference required to fit two pullies, radii $r_1,r_2$ and separation, $d$?

\begin{equation}
l  = \pi \left( r_1 + r_2 \right) + 2\sqrt{ s^2 + \left( r_2 - r_1 \right) ^2 } 
\end{equation}

